0  \'c7i\'f0, kulak t\'fdrmalayan; uyduruk kal\'fdplar. \'d6zg\'fcr \'d6zel k\'fcrs\'fcde bunlar\'fd ustal\'fdkla kullan\'fdyor. \i\ldblquote Bu co\'f0rafyan\'fdn insanlar\'fd\rdblquote , \ldblquote t\'fcm yurtta\'felar\rdblquote\i0 . Bu tav\'fdr rastlant\'fd de\'f0il. Sadece \'d6zg\'fcr \'d6zel de\'f0il, k\'fcrs\'fcye kim \'e7\'fdksa k\'fdvran\'fdyor T\'fcrk dememek i\'e7in.\par
